### Get ticket by ID
GET {{host}}/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Cancel a ticket
POST {{host}}/api/tickets/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update ticket status (Admin only)
POST {{host}}/api/tickets/1/status?status=REFUNDED
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get tickets by event (Admin or Organizer only)
GET {{host}}/api/tickets/event/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get tickets for current user
GET {{host}}/api/tickets/user
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
